{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ensure fair grading for GCSE students in 2024",
        "additional_details": "I want to see change and justice to the education of the youth as the increase of the grade boundaries gives this year's year 11 little time to prepare which is not right. The Government should intervene to help lower the grade boundaries for 2024. The Government should care about the young people of this country.",
        "background": "We want the Government to work with Ofqual to ensure that students in 2024 are graded fairly in light of the lessons learned from students in 2023 who were marked according to pre-pandemic grading.",
